<!--
  Per-waypoint leg: pin {goal} -> {active_goal} once, then replan at 1 Hz to {active_goal}, follow,
  recover with Wait only (retries {active_goal}); no GoalUpdated so live {goal} changes cannot desync replans from the pin.
  Orca4 skips costmap clears. Requires StoreActiveGoal (custom) and any optional ice nodes you add.
  Starting point: navigate_w_replanning_and_recovery.xml
-->

